Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到了许久未见的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我被笼罩在隐隐的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想麻郁先生也是一样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一直不说自己经历的深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我和麻郁先生都决定不去接触她的那部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 由于深衣奈小姐的朋友的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西将会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然实际上应该是两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我们决定了三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,认为这样才是最好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这种不安无论怎样都挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,450)\pos(550,570)\fs40\fn华康少女字体\3c&Ha351c5\bord2}想再跑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我在想“你和朋友之间说了些什么呢”而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谈了许多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 她听说我有亲人的时候 替我感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,高中联赛代表呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在县大会跑出自己的最好成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有种“终于办到了”的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然最兴奋的人是母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 说这种话题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了不该说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,裕香一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了亲人 所以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不和妈妈说好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不说的话 就最好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能够把这当作是圆满收场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我能够回应母亲的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而宫藤能够遇到亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐 该是时候交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,深…深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要泡到昏倒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没面子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要刺激我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我待在这里没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,待在这里也…没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天决定好来晴子家里玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话 一起来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去大闹一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…对不起 我今天有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥还说要亲手做料理的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？可是哥哥做的料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有事情是指你那位朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没和深衣奈在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是 深衣奈小姐好像是去找她朋友 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈的朋友不是那位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是深衣奈小姐的朋友吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,厄…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是深衣奈的家属
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,家属？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方呆坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,问题也不会解决吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 桦恋总是一副担忧的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好麻郁装作一副“不知道”的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 现在还是不想去见裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不…但说不了出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞穂老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为从学校回家时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了宫藤同学走向狱间山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,单身一个女子到这种地方很危险哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可以稍稍在一起一阵子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…瑞穂老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没…那个…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对了…老师…您有丈夫吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是个很棒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚之前发生很多事情的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,结了婚才发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,结了婚才？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有过虽然现在可以一笑置之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过当是可是痛不欲生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那种时候怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,全说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对…从嘴里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把所想的事 全部告诉那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤的事 高兴的事 全部一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的话 能跟我们说说深衣奈小姐的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她本人没说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐她什么都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要问了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不担心深衣奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为担心 就能向别人问深衣奈不愿说的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这样只是减少自己的担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想以这种方式知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙不想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就不应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也认为那样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 叫停了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放心了 宫藤有像你们这样的人陪伴着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家属嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞穂老师 有些事虽然知道自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,却无能为力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不会无能为力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,答案应该找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊…我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,例如 当觉得悲伤的时候 怎么做才能不悲伤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,答案不就已经找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,发现错误的时候 就能看到正确的方向哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那个方向才隐蔽起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,答案已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要前进哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过不要让人担心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他要说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明天放学后 能陪我去一个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要陪你来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是田径场？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有高中联赛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是练习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高中联赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 听过这样的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的那个孩子认识吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩是跑步选手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是长跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是 社•裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我中学同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,关系很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,中学的时候 寄住在她家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,住在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到这里之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没说就离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做离家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我和麻郁一样 在婴儿时就进了孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之后上中学认识了裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为了和田径队的她的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就进了田径部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然自己说有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是挺快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然契机很单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是慢慢地觉得跑步有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在那样的时候 裕香的母亲看中我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,裕香的母亲是有名的田径运动员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有那种钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后阿姨她说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我的监护人到裕香家里一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是拼命地跑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在孤儿院没有什么好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以绝对不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,参加大会 破纪录 得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,之后还有过高中推荐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有奖学金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就能在不对周围的人造成麻烦的情况下跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因故受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不能复原到当运动员的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不能回报阿姨的期望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,推荐也取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在不能再跑的同时 失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法再住在裕香家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的依靠 就只有那张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我很过分吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,推荐决定的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想着打破纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至一起住的裕香也当作劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么裕香一直只用姓氏来称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只想着如何去守住自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不论怎样 也想有个归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你有归宿吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的归宿就是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要勉强地去跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想跑就跑吧 不想跑的话 就别这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你干什么 我和桦恋绝对都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有你必须做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是有理由才来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有理由吧 深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一会儿而已 让我跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤你愿意的话 就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一个即使不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也能保持自我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事 我一定会好好告诉阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有一直妒嫉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,羡慕比我跑得更快的宫藤得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把所有事情告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我当你是我的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真的当作是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁还在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚上工作得很晚的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,家务拜托你了 没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好好去支援裕香小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 到兼职开始的时间我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会三个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人 在这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么好像有些微妙的区别？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对 不同点是房子跟水池之间是有条路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说照片并不是这里照的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在这里后面？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这张照片 是从这个位置照的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 为什么特地跑到这个地方照呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 两个人都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,难道这个屋子才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个屋子才是我们的母亲住的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,370)\fs40\fn华康少女字体\3c&Hb351cf\bord2}想告诉你“喜欢你”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再说“怎么办”这样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道深衣奈小姐在担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道麻郁先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我小野寺桦恋 要把心里的这份心情传达出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,即使让恋爱同盟解散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也要把我这份强烈的感觉传达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Onegai Twins 第十一话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想告诉你“喜欢你”
